title._content: Map of Delaware Bay in vicinity of Cape May

description._content: Creator: Louis W. Hutchins Local number: SIA2012-9674 Summary: Map of Delaware Bay in vicinity of Cape May, noting placement of buoys studied as part of the United States Navy Buoy Fouling Survey, 1943-1947. This material documents the field work of Louis W. Hutchins for the United States Navy Buoy Fouling Survey, 1943 - 1947. Dates: 1943 - 1947 Collection: RU 007248, Louis W. Hutchins Papers, circa 1939-1957 and undated; Box 2, Folder 14. Repository: Smithsonian Institution Archives Related blog post: A Summer Sail View more collections from the Smithsonian Institution.
